data.description: ZERO DOWN financing available! Please ask for details. Great home featuring a HUGE screened-in sun porch with an equally huge open patio! Spacious Primary bedroom with ensuite bath boasts an immense L-shaped walk-in closet. Plus there are sizeable walk-in closets throughout. Lots of flexible living space in this 2500sf home, including a large game room for you to make your own. Fantastic neighborhood has 2 community pools, playgrounds, walking trails, and stocked ponds. The Community Water Park (right across Risinger Rd) wows with amenities such as an Olympic sized pool, kids lagoon, 2 slides, and a nice clubhouse. Conveniently located off the Chisholm Trail Parkway and minutes from all other major highways! Plus it's 5-minutes from the newly proposed HEB on McPherson! Come take a look today!
